description:
App Store Web Site: <a href=" http://itunes.apple.com/fi/app/window-adjustment/id493422927?mt=12" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://itunes.apple.com/fi/app/window-adjustment/id493422927?mt=12</a>


Window Adjustment is a simple window management for OS X.

Features:

* Shrink to Left

* Shrink to Right

* Shrink to Top

* Shrink to Bottom

* Maximize, Full Screen

* Shrink to Center

* Shrink to Top Left

* Shrink to Top Right

* Shrink to Bottom Left

* Shrink to Bottom Right

* Open at Login.

What's New:

* update

* fixed some bug

System Requirements:

Intel Mac, OS X.6 and above
